==Documentation==
This template creates a full franchise page layout with hero section, tabs, wiki content, and sidebar.
Uses Semantic MediaWiki for structured data storage and display.

The page structure follows the classic Giant Bomb wiki design:
* Hero section with cover image, title, and deck
* Tab navigation for sub-pages
* Two-column layout with wiki content and games list on left, franchise details sidebar on right

===Parameters===
{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Parameter !! Description
|-
| Name || Display name of the franchise
|-
| Guid || Giant Bomb API identifier
|-
| Aliases || Alternative names (comma-separated)
|-
| Image || Cover image filename
|-
| Deck || Short description shown in hero
|-
| Games || Games in this franchise (comma-separated page links)
|-
| Characters || Characters in this franchise (comma-separated)
|-
| Concepts || Concepts in this franchise (comma-separated)
|-
| Locations || Locations in this franchise (comma-separated)
|-
| Objects || Objects in this franchise (comma-separated)
|-
| People || People associated with this franchise (comma-separated)
|}

